description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10MIN everyday full body hourglass pilates workout // no equipment // beginner friendly' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: some mornings i dont have time for more so this full body is perfect for those days! love love looove working out outside 

Hope you have fun doing this workout! 

Love u all
